<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: whitesmoke;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #FFAB40;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #FF6F61;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ff8a80;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .button {
                font-size: 1em;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You!</h1>
        <p>We appreciate your time. If you have any feedback, feel free to share it with us. Have a great day!</p>
        <a href="/" class="button">Rejoin</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
